g.text: Level 3 FE Diagram for Updating Staff
Sends HTTP Request to get all Specializations
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Sends HTTP Request to get staff by Id
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Tries to get Staff's Id data
Display Staff's data (autofill form) and Asks for Staff's data
The data can be Email and/or Phone Number and/or Specialization Name
Sends HTTP Request to update Staff's data with the new data
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Validates Staff's data and tries to update Staff's data
